The paper discusses a testing methodology for Deep Learning (DL) systems, which falls under the software engineering (cs.SE) category. The paper also mentions the ability of DL systems to solve complex tasks such as image recognition and machine translation, which are typical applications of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses the effectiveness of the proposed methodology on multiple DL datasets, which falls under the machine learning (cs.LG) category. The paper also mentions the need for testing DL systems in safety- and security-critical applications, which falls under the cryptography and security (cs.CR) and systems and control (cs.SY) categories.
